OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFine and chilly to start with
OL,6,Fsome sunshine, however cloud soon
OL,7,Fthickening from the west, ahead of
OL,8,Fspells of rain and increasingly strong
OL,9,Fwinds spreading in towards lunchtime.
OL,10,FWinds strengthening to inland gales
OL,11,Fduring the afternoon, although mild in
OL,12,Fshelter.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FBecoming very windy, with
OL,15,Finland gales, perhaps severe for a
OL,16,Ftime, coupled with heavy rain and
OL,17,Fblustery showers. Becoming drier and
OL,18,Fclearer through the early hours, with
OL,19,Fwinds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
