OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA colder-feeling day, bright
OL,6,Fand breezy with some sunny spells for
OL,7,Fa time. Cloudier with further rain or
OL,8,Fshowers during the afternoon, clearing
OL,9,Fin turn to late sunshine. Winds easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,12,Ffine through this period, with some
OL,13,Fwarm days and sunny periods after
OL,14,Fchilly starts. Perhaps becoming more
OL,15,Funsettled from the west midweek.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
